### Test 1: Student viewing unenrolled course (should deny)
POST http://localhost:3000/course-access
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "student",
  "action": "view",
  "enrolled": false
}

###

### Test 2: Instructor updating course as owner (should grant)
POST http://localhost:3000/course-access
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "instructor",
  "action": "update",
  "owner": true
}

###

### Test 3: Instructor updating course as non-owner (should deny)
POST http://localhost:3000/course-access
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "instructor",
  "action": "update",
  "owner": false
}

###

### Test 4: Guest viewing non-free course (should deny)
POST http://localhost:3000/course-access
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "guest",
  "action": "view",
  "free": false
}

###

### Test 5: Instructor deleting published course as owner (should deny)
POST http://localhost:3000/course-access
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "instructor",
  "action": "delete",
  "owner": true,
  "published": true
}
